 The negative CD has the following information: America — cohesive AOR greatest‑hits: warm 1970s analogue midrange, acoustic‑driven mid‑tempo songs with close, natural midrange vocals; inventive multitracked crystal harmonies, restrained guitar/organ; low compression, revealing quiet moments, precise sequencing ideal for listeners who prefer melodic, harmony‑forward start‑to‑finish listening.

