- Preferences: cohesive, album‑oriented records; warm analog sheen; layered, harmonized vocals/guitars; spacious stereo imaging; anthemic choruses; polished, dynamic mixes; extended, emotionally charged title performances and sequencing that reward start‑to‑finish listening; intimate, lyric‑forward vocals placed clearly in the mix; arrangements that breathe and evolve; preserved dynamics and transparent mastering; strong melodies.  
